Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE

Name: Total time spent on processes leading to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE in re-submission processes

Name: Total time for processes to be restarted after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR

Name: Minimum time to restart the process after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
